summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Thirty-fourth Avenue from East Pike Street to East Denny Way et al, in the City of Seattle, grading & curbing under Ordinance No. 15499, creating Local Improvement District No. 1422 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
